# StackOverflowLite API Documentation

StackOverflow-lite is a platform where people can ask questions and provide answers to questions.

## Users Signup [/auth/signup]

### Register a user [POST]


+ Request (application/json)

            {
              "fullName": "string",
              "email": "string",
              "password": "string"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

         

    + Body

            {
                  "message": "string",
                  "newUser": {
                      "fullName": "string",
                    "email": "string"
                  }
                }


+ Response 400 (application/json)
              
              bad request
                        {
                "success": false,
                "message":  "string"
                }

+ Response 409 (application/json)
               
               Conflict in resource
               
                        {
                "success": false,
                "message":  "string"
                }


