##  Questions  [/questions]


### Get all questions  [GET]


+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

         

    + Body
                
                              {
                    "success": true,
                    "message": "string",
                    "newQuestion": {
                        "questionTopic": "string",
                        "questionBody": "string"
                    }
                }


+ Response 400 (application/json)
              
              bad request(There is no question with this ID)
                        {
                "success": false,
                "message":  "string"
                }


